      • getLineFilter

        java.util.regex.Pattern getLineFilter()
        This method should return a Pattern. This Pattern (regular expression) is used to filter the lines of the LogStream /log-file. Only for lines matching this expression the method onNewLine(LogLine) or onNewBlockOfLines(List) is called providing the matching line of the log-file.
